review.title: Click clack, click clack. Buy this keyboard, and don’t look back!
review.review: I am a writer, and I require something quite “clicky”. If you are like me, then think no further. Buy this keyboard and click-clack your way to glory. I would buy it 10 more times if I could, I seriously love this keyboard. I’m sure it would even make a fantastic (but loud) gaming keyboard as well. But I only use it for one thing. Ironically I wrote this review on my phone, not with the keyboard.
